        (4) A person appointed under this section shall perform such functions as may be specified in the instrument of his or her appointment and such other functions as the Authority may from time to time determine.
        (5) A person appointed under this section is not, by virtue of his or her appointment for the purposes of this Act, subject to the State Service Act 2000 .
